{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"互換性の情報源","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Compatibility_sources","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下の情報源が SVG 要素と属性の互換性の確認に活用できます。</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/SVG_1.1_Support_in_Firefox\">https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/SVG_in_Firefox</a> Firefoxに対する改編履歴あり</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.webkit.org/projects/svg/status.xml\" rel=\" noopener\">http://www.webkit.org/projects/svg/status.xml</a> WebKit, Safari, Chrome 向けの<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://wayback.archive.org/web/*/http://www.webkit.org/projects/svg/status.xml\" rel=\" noopener\">記録書庫</a></li>\n <li>Opera 9 以降向けの追加情報は <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.opera.com/docs/specs/opera9/svg/\" rel=\" noopener\">http://www.opera.com/docs/specs/opera9/svg/</a> 、 Opera 8向けは <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.opera.com/docs/specs/opera8/\" rel=\" noopener\">http://www.opera.com/docs/specs/opera8/</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://blogs.msdn.com/b/ie/archive/2010/03/18/svg-in-ie9-roadmap.aspx\" rel=\" noopener\">http://blogs.msdn.com/b/ie/archive/2010/03/18/svg-in-ie9-roadmap.aspx</a> IE9 向けの対応状況へのヒント</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.codedread.com/svg-support.php\" rel=\" noopener\">Codedread.com における SV G対応図</a> W3C スイートに対する基本確認事項</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scalable_Vector_Graphics\" rel=\" noopener\">Wikipedia</a> 基本的な情報 (規格標準ではない)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"以下の情報源が SVG 要素と属性の互換性の確認に活用できます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Compatibility sources","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Sources des compatibilités","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Compatibility sources","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source